\displaystyle S=\sum_{k=1}^\infty {k\over 2^k}
\displaystyle {S\over 2} = \sum_{k=1}^\infty {k\over 2*2^k} = \sum_{k=1}^\infty {k\over 2^{k+1}} = \sum_{l=2}^\infty {l-1\over 2^l} = \sum_{l=1}^\infty {l-1\over 2^l}
l=1
